This paper is likely to belong to the Robotics (cs.RO) sub-category as it deals with the evaluation of highly automated vehicles. It also involves the use of statistical models and simulation, which are common in Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), and Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-categories. Additionally, the evaluation of automated vehicles involves control systems, which is a topic covered in the Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-category.
